  <summary date="2017-09-11T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">No Knives on Planes Act of 2017

This bill prohibits the Department of Homeland Security from implementing any change to the prohibited items list of the Transportation Security Administration that would permit passengers to carry small, non-locking knives through passenger screening checkpoints at airports, into sterile areas at airports, or onboard passenger aircraft.</summary>
